{"id":196669,"type":6,"name":"The Amazing Race","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e5/aa/196669_w2Awd.jpg","summary":"“极速前进（The Amazing Race，TAR）”是一个一群人环游世界进行竞速比赛的真人秀节目。CBS从2001年开始按季播出。节目记录多对选手在一个月中进行的环球竞赛。\r\n整个比赛分为多个赛段进行，其中淘汰赛段的最后一名出局，直到剩下最后三对选手（第25、26季是4支队伍）完成最后的对决，冠军可以获得100万美元的奖金。比赛起始点均在美国，中间经过世界多个国家。各队必须按制作方给出的路线资讯指引周游世界，并在赛程中完成规定的任务。\r\n自艾美奖2003年设立黄金时段艾美奖最佳竞技类真人秀（Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Reality-Competition Program）以来，极速前进“十三提十中”，获得这一殊荣（2003-2009，2011-2012，2014年）。 \r\n目前，包括美国，共有13个国家或地区制作了14个当地的版本。（不包含终止拍摄的中欧版）。\r\n极速前进已有两个不同的国内引进版本，分别是2010-12年上海外语频道的《极速前进：冲刺中国》与2014-15年深圳卫视的《极速前进》。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>极速前进</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>三</li><li><span>别名: </span>驚險大挑戰</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>奪寶奇Show</li><li><span>集数: </span>13</li><li><span>开始: </span>2001-09-05</li><li><span>结束: </span>2001-12-13</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>每集长: </span>43m</li><li><span>电视网: </span>CBS</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>www.cbs.com/shows/amazing_race</li>","collection":{"wish":1},"tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":675226,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675226","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675227,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675227","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675228,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675228","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675229,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675229","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675230,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675230","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675231,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/675231","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":675